					<h2 id="tashi-delek">The Universal Hello: Tashi Delek <span class="tibetan-text">བཀྲ་ཤིས་བདེ་ལེགས།</span></h2>
					<p>Forget searching for ten different ways to say hello. In Tibetan, one phrase fits all: <strong>Tashi Delek</strong>. (<span class="tibetan-text">བཀྲ་ཤིས་བདེ་ལེགས།</span>)</p>
					<p>It's far more than a simple "hi." It carries the beautiful meaning of "auspicious wishes" or "may all good things come to you." You can use it to greet anyone, at any time of day.</p>

					<div class="example-box rounded-2xl p-6 my-6">
